ChangeLog
---------

06-10-2007	fidesratio	Modified and (improved?) the GSB_CFLAGS/tuning in generic.SlackBuild. (1.3)
                                Updated all gnome.platform SlackBuilds to 1.3.
                                
05-10-2007 	fidesratio      Updated all gnome.platform SlackBuilds to 1.2.
                		Created patch for avahi+dbus < 1.1.1.  See README in directory.
				Updated a52dec, faac, faad2, ffmpeg, x264, libdvdcss, libcdio, libcddb SlackBuilds.
				Added yasm (needed by x264).

02/10/07	tadgy		Added lib/gsb lib/perl/GSBv2.
				Moved template files from scripts/ to lib/gsb/.
				Updated/edited more documentation.
				Centralized Changelog. Please follow this format. 

30-09-2007      fidesratio	Added gnome.applications, and split from gnome.desktop.
				Applied changes to generic.SlackBuild from tadgy (rev. generic.SlackBuild 1.2)
				Updated a52dec, ffmpeg, xvidcore, faac, faad2, lame.
                		Updated libcdio, vcdimager, libcddb.
                		Added libexif, libexif-gtk, libopenraw, libiptcdata, gtkunique to gnome.libraries.

29-09-2007      fidesratio	Updated libgnome, libgnomeui, libbonoboui, libgnomecanvas, gnome-keyring.
                		Updated pygtk, libdaemon, dbus-python, avahi, gnome-vfs, intltool.
                		Removed gnome-vfs-monikers.
                		Added scrollkeeper, gtk-engines, gnome-common to gnome.platform.
                		Added icon-naming-utils to gnome.platform.
                		Few small fixes in generic.SlackBuild.
                		Fixed build hang with parallel builds in ORBit2.

28-09-2007      fidesratio	Updated GConf, gnome-mime-data, pygobject, pyorbit, pycairo

27-09-2007      fidesratio	Updated libbonoboui
				Added a generic.SlackBuild as a template for other SlackBuilds.

26-09-2007      fidesratio	Changed partial build order for gnome.platform.SlackBuild.
                		Changed orbit2 to ORBit2.
                		Created generic.SlackBuild with fuller package build options, variables
                  		     and consolidated several options found in other SlackBuilds.
                		Inital trunk for GSB Gnome2.20.x

